videos.description: Daniel Gafford elevates and goes straight through Kyle Kuzma, sending him to the deck as he throws down a powerful dunk in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gafford runs over Kuzma for destructive dunk) 2021/04/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gafford runs over Kuzma for destructive dunk

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker wisely gets out of the way at the last second as Chandler Hutchison takes flight to demolish the rim on a powerful fast-break dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (THT dodges posterizing dunk by Hutchison, Wizards' bench loves it) 2021/04/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: THT dodges posterizing dunk by Hutchison, Wizards' bench loves it

videos.description: Anthony Davis tries to block Rui Hachimura's dunk but fails as he gets posterized and takes a shot to the face and ends up on the floor.
